ebus Daemon (ebusd) - NEWS
==========================

2013-03-01:
* Add documentation and an example command csv file.

2013-02-28:
* Add loglevel as telnet command to change logging level at runtime.

2013-02-27:
* Add new config parameter print_size to adjust number of bytes at output stream.

2013-02-22:
* Changed client answer code so normal telnet client can handle it

2013-02-21:
* Improve decoding of cyc commands to all ebus message types.

2013-02-19:
* Add some usefull description of ebusd to README

2013-02-17:
* Add csv tool to print command configuration.
* Add deconding of cyc commands.

2013-02-16:
* Structure for commands improved so only one structure for GET/SET/CYC is needed
* Possible formats for GET / SET (asc, bcd, d1b, d1c, d2b, d2c, dat, tim)

2013-02-06:
* Fix some malfunctions of command decode function
* Add parameter send_retry so the daemon can try x times to send command

2013-02-04:
* Add the ability to send commands via telnet to daemon
  (This ist just added for GET and a few ebus commands for response)

2013-02-01:
* Add functions to read ebus command files

2013-01-25:
* Add autogen.sh script in main dir
* Logging functions changed from level to class system

2013-01-24:
* Add example daemon configuration file
* Add functions for parsing daemon configuration file

2013-01-17:
* Prepare Source to compile with GNU Autotools
